flowchart TD
    subgraph P[Project Bootstrap]
        P1[Owner calls registerProjectV2 or registerProjectV3]
        P2[BountyHub stores project mode deadlines rules]
        P3[Project vnetStatus set to Pending]
        P4[Emit ProjectRegisteredV2]
        P10[P10 Workflow records commit window for project]
        P11[P11 Workflow schedules cron countdown by commit deadline]
